    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "数字是<strong>离散且唯一</strong>的 $\\to$ 不好直接求 $[min, max]$ 范围。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "题目让 $ans[1]$ 尽可能大，等价于尽量减少排在根节点数字 $ans[1]$ 后面的叶子数量。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "故设 $dp[u]$：<strong>要保证</strong> $u$ <strong>拿到一个尽可能大的数，最少会有多少个数被迫排在</strong> $u$ <strong>的后面（包括</strong> $u$ <strong>的数字本身）。</strong> <em>（这个状态还真是，非常难想到）</em>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "然后就是对 $max$ 和 $min$ 分别考虑<strong>状态转移</strong>：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "heading": "情况 A：$u$ 是 <code>max</code> 节点",
          "level": 4,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<code>max</code> 节点就像一个<strong>“只要一个好，全家都光荣”</strong>的家长。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>结论</strong>：$u$ 只需要选一个最给力的儿子，最给力：排在后面的数最少。所以：$dp[u] = \\min(dp[son1], dp[son2]...)$。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "情况 B：$u$ 是 <code>min</code> 节点",
          "level": 4,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<code>min</code> 节点就像一个<strong>“只要一个差，全家都完蛋”</strong>的家长。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "为了让 <code>min</code> 节点的值大，你必须保证它的<strong>每一个</strong>儿子都拿到大数。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "你要满足所有子节点取到大数，才能保证最小值不掉下去。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>结论</strong>：$u$ 必须背负所有儿子的压力，所以：$dp[u] = \\sum(dp[son])$。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "情况 C：叶子节点",
          "level": 4,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "能排在叶子节点本身及其后面的数只有其本身，所以 $dp[u] = 1$。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "int dp[N];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\tvar ops = vector<int>(n + 1);\n\tvar g = vector<vector<int>>(n + 1);\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> ops[i];\n\tfa(i, 2, n) {\n\t\tint f; cin >> f;\n\t\tg[f].pb(i); g[i].pb(f);\n\t}\n\tint k = 0;\n\tfa(i, 2, n)if (g[i].size() == 1)k++;\n\n\tvar dfs = [&](var dfs, int now, int fa)->void {\n\t\tif (now != 1 and g[now].size() == 1) { \n\t\t\tdp[now] = 1;\n\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t}\n\t\tint sum = 0, mn = INF;\n\t\tfor (int to : g[now]) {\n\t\t\tif (to == fa)continue;\n\t\t\tdfs(dfs, to, now);\n\t\t\tmn = min(mn, dp[to]);\n\t\t\tsum += dp[to];\n\t\t}\n\t\tif (ops[now])dp[now] = mn;\n\t\telse dp[now] = sum;\n\t\t};\n\tdfs(dfs, 1, 0);\n\tcout << k - dp[1] + 1 << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
